{"tid":1915974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沈旭暉開左個youtube channel, 大家一齊去訂閱!!","createTime":"2020-03-08T14:58:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T16:14:45.000Z","uid":49643,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2d64d87695f973d3f7caea1c37cfb9928626d1a4","tid":1915974,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T14:58:29.000Z","msg":"堅離地城：沈旭暉國際生活台 Simon's Glos World<br />\n25分鐘 &middot; <br />\n【#官方公告🌍】終於都係拍咗段簡單teaser，學人開定個YouTube Channel。知道內容一定好悶，加上自己始終唔享受講嘢，所以每段都會好短幾分鐘咁，雖然前輩溫馨提示話咁會無廣告，但是但啦。至於內容有邊幾類，仲構思緊，希望大家比啲意見，有緣歡迎subscribe，感謝感謝。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCXf8jlTSP9kp6g4ROCfgvbQ/featured\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCXf8jlTSP9kp6g4ROCfgvbQ%2Ffeatured&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5Bw0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=d368937a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCXf8jlTSP9kp6g4ROCfgvbQ/featured</a>"},{"pid":"bc1b5d89365b6802e7549631d2d32436522500e0","tid":1915974,"uid":49643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T14:59:19.000Z","msg":"堅離地球 &middot; 沈旭暉<br />\n1.09K 位訂閱者<br />\n<br />\n【堅離地球 &middot; 沈旭暉】點解拍YouTube？<br />\n<br />\n作為一個從來都唔識應付鏡頭嘅人，設立個人YouTube channel的確係好大膽嘅project。但始終新時代就有新時代嘅平台，希望有咗呢個YouTube channel，可以觸及到更多對國際關係同未來學有興趣嘅朋友。<br />\n<br />\n大家睇完記得三步CLS：Comment、Like、Share。<br />\n<br />\np.s. 連登會員「大雞樂」記得同伯友分享我嘅YouTube channel，感謝。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yD6KsQvMzB0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyD6KsQvMzB0&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5Bw0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=69f9c52e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yD6KsQvMzB0</a>"},{"pid":"fa7857d8eaa8ffce39f0512c105d244630211d1c","tid":1915974,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T14:59:36.000Z","msg":"肯定好快黃標"},{"pid":"12187aaf0d290cf0ae5356c86a1fa40c6c11b890","tid":1915974,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T15:00:29.000Z","m